        <abstract>
            <p>All his advisers agree that CD ought not to take notice of Butler’s attack.</p> 
<p>F. M. Balfour has offered to translate EK’s reply to Butler and to send it to <hi rend="italic">Nature</hi>. [The letter was published in <hi rend="italic">Nature</hi> 23 (1881): 288.]</p> 
        </abstract>
